      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 48 },
      "id": 7,
      "options": {
        "content": "| Backend | Best for | Avoid when |\n|---|---|---|\n| **MinIO + PostgreSQL** | Mixed retrieval, explorer UI, curation with blob fetch | Cost-sensitive hot paths |\n| **Redis** | Sub-ms metadata lookup, embedding cache, hot-path serving | Full-payload blob retrieval, large disk budgets |\n| **Lance** | Random-access evaluation, curation workflows, Arrow-native pipelines | Sequential-only training loops |\n| **Parquet** | Analytical scans, cheap interchange, columnar queries | Point lookups, streaming training |\n| **WebDataset** | High-throughput sequential training (DALI / PyTorch DataLoader) | Random access, curation, any point query |",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Backend Selection Guide",
      "type": "text"
    },
